node.text:
If you don’t know by now, I really love to eat fish! 🐠🐟 This recipe is slightly different from the usual ones.

https://youtu.be/CXXVO39w_-w
@eat.kae.love this recipe not bad if you are sick of the usual steam and plain deep fried method. 😊
@happyzboys okok! I will check out the YouTube recipe! Please share more ideas to cook!
@alfee hi dear, here is the link to the video: https://youtu.be/CXXVO39w_-w  On top of spring onion and ginger, this recipe uses garlic too. Hope this helps!
Do you mind to tell me what did you put on the fish to steam? It looks different than what we make in HK. We normally put ginger and spring onion only. Yours looks really yummy !
